<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<svg width="250" height="50" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" >
  <style>
    .penguin{
        animation:move var(--num) infinite linear;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px white);
    }
    .igloo{
        transform: scale(2.15) translate(0, -22px);
    }
    @keyframes move {
         from { transform: translate(250px, 0px); }
         to {  transform: translate(0px, 0px); }
    }
  </style>
  <image id="penguin" style="--num:20s;" x="15" y="23" width="20" height="19" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
  <image y="22" class="igloo" width="20" height="20" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
  <use href="#penguin" style="--num:8s;" x="0" y="0" class="penguin" />
  <use href="#penguin" style="--num:9s;" x="0" y="0" class="penguin" />
  <use href="#penguin" style="--num:12s;" x="0" y="0" class="penguin" />
</svg>
